Frequently asked questions

Expand all

With Unlimited Your Way for Business, you can pick a plan for each line in your plan group.At least one phone line is required in the plan group to add other non-phone lines. A maximum of 10 lines allowed per Unlimited Your Way for Business plan group.

When you add more phone lines to an Unlimited Your Way plan group the monthly price per line goes down. This discount applies to the first five or six lines depending which plan you choose.

No. While you can have a combination of phone lines and non-phone devices in a plan group, only phone lines impact your price per phone line.

Yes, you can add all non-phone devices that work with our legacy Business Unlimited plans to an Unlimited Your Way for Business plan group. This also includes mobile hotspot devices. But plans for laptops and mobile hotspot devices arent unlimited. Instead, these plans have a 15GB data allowance, with a data overage charge of $10 for each additional 2GB of data.

Our plans dont offer unlimited hotspot data. AT&T Business Unlimited Advanced plan delivers 100GB of hotspot data for each line. Remember that youll need a device that works with mobile hotspot data and that after you use 100GByour hotspot speed will slow down to 128Kbps max.

Yes, simply sign in to your myATT account or Premier account to explore your change plan options.

AT&T ActiveArmoradvanced mobile security is included with the Business Unlimited Premium 2.0, Business Unlimited Performance plans. It offers:

  • Personal ID Monitor: Provides alerts and helpful tips if your personal info is leaked.
  • Safe Browsing: Blocks suspicious sites so you can surf the web safely.
  • Secure Wi-Fi VPN: Creates your own private connection to protect your data on public Wi-Fi networks.
  • Wi-Fi Alerts: Notifies you when a Wi-Fi network you join may be dangerous to your privacy.
  • Breach Reports: Informs you about corporate data breaches with tips on how to remedy.
  • Theft Alerts: Notifies you via email if suspicious activity is detected on your phone (Android only).
  • Fraud call detection and blocking: Identifies and blocks likely fraudulent calls.
  • Spam calls alerts: Notifies you of telemarketers and suspected spam calls.
  • Personal Block List: Allows you to add individual unwanted callers to your own block list. Disclosure: Settings can be adjusted in the app.
  • Caller ID: Lets you know the name of who is calling before you answer.

AT&T ActiveArmorstandard mobile security is included with the AT&T Business Unlimited Starter wireless plan. Plan highlights:

  • Helps ensure your device is secure and protected.
  • Provides important alerts about security for your device.
  • Delivers updates about corporate breaches that could affect your personal data.
  • Detects and blocks likely fraudulent calls.
  • Alerts you of telemarketers and suspected spam calls.
  • Allows you to add individual unwanted callers to your own block list with Personal Block List. Disclosure: Settings can be adjusted in the app.

All plans for phones include unlimited calling from the U.S. to Mexico and Canada and unlimited text from the U.S. to over 200 countries. When in Mexico and Canada, you can also talk, text and use data with no roaming charges. Roaming may be at 2G speeds. Pay-per-use rates apply to calls from the U.S. to other countries unless you have an add-on. Learn more
